<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .credentials {
      background: #e9ecef;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    .warning {
      color: #856404;
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome as a Delegate!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
    
    <p>You have been invited to join {{companyName}} as a delegate user. Your account has been created with the following credentials:</p>
    
    <div class="credentials">
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
      <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{tempPassword}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="warning">
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> This is your login password. You can change it anytime from your profile settings.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>You can access your delegate account here:</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>As a delegate, you have access to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Delegated permissions and access</li>
      <li>Company resources based on your delegation</li>
      <li>Profile management</li>
      <li>Communication tools</li>
    </ul>
    
    {{#if expirationDate}}
    <div class="warning">
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> Your delegate access will expire on {{expirationDate}}.</p>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your company administrator.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>{{companyName}} Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent automatically. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>You can change your password anytime from your profile settings after logging in.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 